OL,5,G1600 The Winslow Boy
OL,6,     F1948. Drama. Directed by Anthony
OL,7,     FAsquith. Stars Robert Donat,
OL,8,     FCedric Hardwicke & Basil Radford.
OL,9,     FPre-WWI England, a youngster is
OL,10,     Fexpelled from a naval academy for
OL,11,     Ftheft. His parents demand a trial.
OL,12,G1820 Strange But True?
OL,13,     FChingle Hall/Psychic Detective:
OL,14,     FPart 1. 1996. Michael Aspel
OL,15,     Fexplores the ghostly presence at
OL,16,     Fthe 700 year old manor house
OL,17,     FChingle Hall and the baffling
OL,18,     Fstory of American psychic Dixie
OL,19,     FYetarian.
